{"_id":"bPDAhCFEP5Jvybhg","name":"Conditions","permission":{"default":0,"hg1bBCAUsIDPKim6":3},"folder":"","flags":{"exportSource":{"world":"SF_AG-OP","system":"starfinder","coreVersion":"0.6.0","systemVersion":"0.2.5"}},"content":"<h1>Starfinder; Conditions (SRD)</h1>\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; border-width: 100%;\">\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; margin-top: 0in; margin-left: 0in; width: 2.7215in;\">\n<div style=\"direction: ltr; margin-top: 0in; margin-left: 0in; width: 2.7215in;\">\n<div style=\"direction: ltr;\">\n<table style=\"width: 600px; border-color: #a3a3a3; border-style: solid; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" title=\"\" border=\"0\" summary=\"\" cellspacing=\"5\" cellpadding=\"5\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 227px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[5h1DEvrNSbFGZNNg]{Asleep} You take a -10 penalty to Perception checks to notice things.</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 279px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[WocmfZGfzK68Ktqt]{Bleeding} You take the listed damage at the beginning of your turn.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 227px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[OYsra4CxzCYng2vP]{Blinded} You're flat-footed, you take a -4 penalty to most Str- and Dex-based skill checks and opposed Perception checks, you automatically fail Perception checks based on sight, opponents have total concealment against you, and you must succeed at a DC 10 Acrobatics check to move faster than half speed or else fall prone.</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 279px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">@JournalEntry[0GyNgmlL1ruk21hT]{Broken}&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px;\">Weapon: attack and damage rolls take a -2 penalty and can't deal extra effects on a critical hit; armor: AC bonuses are halved </span></span><span><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px;\">and the armor check penalty is doubled; vehicle: -2 penalty to AC, collision DC, and Piloting modifier, and it halves its full </span></span><span><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px;\">speed and MPH; tool or tech that provides bonuses: bonuses are halved.</span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 227px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[sIGfVwdao9xiw945]{Burning} You take the listed fire damage each round, and you must be extinguished to end the condition.</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 279px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[qgy90uGrUlxIkU98]{Confused} You treat all creatures as enemies, and you must roll on the table to determine your actions.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 227px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[5VqPLGUlVoFXTSXe]{Cowering} You're flat-footed and can take no actions.</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 279px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[bBiGzP1rhhARX80k]{Dazed} You can take no actions.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 227px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[v8PIkefWbra68drN]{Dazzled} You take a -1 penalty to attack rolls and sight-based Perception checks.</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 279px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[wkjFrkSq0hdRQa4E]{Dead} Your soul leaves your body, you can't act in any way, and you can't benefit from normal or magical healing.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 227px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[LCUFdBkYtrj8T0OP]{Deafened} You take a -4 penalty to initiative checks and opposed Perception checks, and you automatically fail sound-based Perception checks.</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 279px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[MVBMm8wVgogHOgoA]{Dying} You're unconscious, you can take no actions, and you must stabilize or lose Resolve Points and potentially die.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 227px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[9JrKEulKQFXsAvRn]{Encumbered} Speeds are reduced by 10 feet, maximum Dex bonus to AC is reduced to +2, and you take a -5 penalty to Str- and Dex-based checks.</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 279px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">@JournalEntry[WlTBemZ2tCTCkNcv]{Entangled}&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px;\">You move at half speed; you cannot run or charge; and you take a -2 penalty to AC, attack rolls, Reflex saves, initiative checks, </span></span><span><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px;\">and Dex-based skill and ability checks.</span></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 227px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;\">@JournalEntry[z7p4znIkXBRa77V7]{Exhausted}&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px;\">You move at half speed; you cannot run or charge; you take a -3 penalty to AC, attack rolls, melee damage rolls, Reflex saves, </span></span><span><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px;\">initiative checks, and Str- and Dex-based skill and ability checks; and you reduce your encumbered limit by 3 bulk.</span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 279px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[JYjCbPmdWuSDGdit]{Fascinated} You must pay attention to the fascinating effect and take a -4 penalty to skill checks made as reactions.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 227px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[9QOqzHsNpwE71a7w]{Fatigued} You cannot run or charge; you take a -1 penalty to AC, attack rolls, melee damage rolls, Reflex saves, initiative checks, and Str- and Dex-based skill and ability checks; and you reduce your encumbered limit by 1 bulk.</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 279px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[iUL3YRb1si86KbIm]{Flat-Footed} You take a -2 penalty to AC, and you cannot take reactions or make attacks of opportunity.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 227px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[EswTt1YlkHfD3rgQ]{Frightened} You must flee or fight, and you take a -2 penalty to ability checks, attack rolls, saving throws, and skill checks.</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 279px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[o5YaXdWGbGKZlgXI]{Grappled} You cannot move or take two-handed actions; you take a -2 penalty to AC, most attack rolls, Reflex saves, initiative checks, and Dex-based skill and ability checks; and you cannot make attacks of opportunity.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 227px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[0E2wl3HXx18NPWqN]{Helpless} Your Dex modifier is -5, and melee attacks against you gain a +4 bonus.</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 279px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[nxG9yAzDNA7JXEMs]{Nauseated} You're unable to attack, cast spells, or concentrate on spells, and the only action you can take is a single move action per turn.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 227px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[TtX4u5NKPAUvk8zu]{Off-Kilter} You can't take move actions except to right yourself, you take a -2 penalty to attacks, and you're flat-footed.</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 279px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[Clluwq5mbTcUWvud]{Off-Target} You take a -2 penalty to attack rolls.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 227px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[CJUsFX8UbrZ2w8yE]{Overburdened} Speeds are reduced to 5 feet; maximum Dex bonus to AC is reduced to +0; and you take a -5 penalty to Str- and Dex-based checks.</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 279px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[DauWgEHRFUraeP1U]{Panicked} You drop all held items; you flee at top speed; you cannot take other actions; you take a -2 penalty to ability checks, saving throws, and skill checks; and you cower if cornered.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 227px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[vj63WubjCJceyWfb]{Paralyzed} Your Dex modifier is -5, and you cannot move but can take mental actions.</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 279px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[hIUBm6QHQLWFP557]{Pinned} You cannot move, you're flat-footed, and you take penalties to the same attributes as for grappled but the penalty is -4.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 227px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[ytdsLTJCKP1Djb5q]{Prone} You take a -4 penalty to melee attacks, a +4 bonus to AC against ranged attacks, and a -4 penalty to AC against melee attacks.</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 279px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[nxLhfxvlvH3zTGVv]{Shaken} You take a -2 penalty to ability checks, attack rolls, saving throws, and skill checks.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 227px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[wGUjEiCf4jjDVNDh]{Sickened} You take a -2 penalty to ability checks, attack rolls, weapon damage rolls, saving throws, and skill checks.</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 279px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[hqGLI2AHoxdyZKZD]{Stable} You're no longer dying, but you are still unconscious.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 227px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[OBxIUd2xsKlyNHig]{Staggered} You can take only a single move or standard action each round and can't take reactions, but you can take swift actions as normal.</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 279px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[B4Yv84wuvrDjhzNh]{Stunned} You drop everything held, you can't take actions, and you're flat-footed.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16px;\">\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 227px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">@JournalEntry[aAc7SLkjLyJRaJ51]{Unconscious} You're knocked out and helpless.</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align: top; width: 279px; padding: 2pt 3pt; height: 16px; border: 1pt solid #a3a3a3;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0in; font-size: 11.0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"}
